{"tid":2094314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"古埃及有帝王谷；美國有總統山；中國點解無主席？","createTime":"2020-07-04T13:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T08:56:53.000Z","uid":17008,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c92fe30fc0cb30b8edb9a596d5aba9d0667ba2","tid":2094314,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"古埃及 人類史最強古代帝國<br />\n美國 人類史最強民主國<br />\n中國 人類史古往今來最強國<br />\n<br />\n一，秦始王 嬴大 <br />\n統一天下<br />\n二，成吉思汗 鐵大 <br />\n為將來尸中國橫跨歐亞非 史上最大國打下基礎<br />\n三，毛澤東 毛大 <br />\n完成人類史最大社會改革 寫下毛語錄影響後世<br />\n四，習近平，習大 <br />\n完成人類史最大工業革命 中華民族偉大復興 促成人類命運共同體"},{"pid":"209c67c2232dbbe8155e445ac053c5f8ebd7ae04","tid":2094314,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"15世紀之前，中華文化的確係世界上最優秀文化，此後漸漸沒落"},{"pid":"82771654ef56bc55036643771d5f60869d3e9472","tid":2094314,"uid":6063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"因為中國偉人會留條全屍比後人儋仰遺容<br />\n<br />\n毛臘肉"},{"pid":"e43cc7a06423feca32cdf18b8c31714fd1c4efe4","tid":2094314,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"209c67c2232dbbe8155e445ac053c5f8ebd7ae04","tid":2094314,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"15世紀之前，中華文化的確係世界上最優秀文化，此後漸漸沒落"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"不敢苟同 點解你咁講？"},{"pid":"36e244de5a4797eacd8cc127927dbc08adadf0a1","tid":2094314,"uid":4575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"有個主席玻璃箱"},{"pid":"8731ca648834097c3d5284ecec43b954c9d27060","tid":2094314,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"清遠也有古龍峽巨猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2q1r2r4/ctp-vzntr/1537423716978p8nonn19q2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2q1r2r4